    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327640/extras/2ec5d1b2a450f59f4d9365ef33b9b636.poster.avif?t=1771250516\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327640/extras/2ec5d1b2a450f59f4d9365ef33b9b636.webm?t=1771250516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327640/extras/2ec5d1b2a450f59f4d9365ef33b9b636.mp4?t=1771250516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >参加自动战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >位置非常关键：战斗结果取决于你的战前设置、角色能力和你的命令。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327640/extras/69a5c1cc9e4ef138e9044a508eb73ff3.poster.avif?t=1771250516\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327640/extras/69a5c1cc9e4ef138e9044a508eb73ff3.webm?t=1771250516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327640/extras/69a5c1cc9e4ef138e9044a508eb73ff3.mp4?t=1771250516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >利用环境</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让战场变成你的优势：建造尖刺墙，在城市废墟中建立阻塞点，将敌人诱入陷阱，将他们推向危险地带或地雷。谁说这种手段不公平？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327640/extras/d90d47b614f3814a2fe5ad09f33060d1.poster.avif?t=1771250516\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327640/extras/d90d47b614f3814a2fe5ad09f33060d1.webm?t=1771250516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327640/extras/d90d47b614f3814a2fe5ad09f33060d1.mp4?t=1771250516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >组建你的小队</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >指挥一支由各种各样的角色组成的队伍，学习如何使用他们的能力和战斗形态，并利用强大的植入体和装备（如能量护盾和时间武器）来增强他们的实力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327640/extras/f5749e47a3d901afe8d54f2bc5362225.poster.avif?t=1771250516\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327640/extras/f5749e47a3d901afe8d54f2bc5362225.webm?t=1771250516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327640/extras/f5749e47a3d901afe8d54f2bc5362225.mp4?t=1771250516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >了解你的敌人</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抵御致命的劫掠者，智取叛变者，猎杀危险的外星人，获取战利品和荣誉。各种敌人、地形和战斗目标都要求你随机应变。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327640/extras/3ac3eb9db6f903c2ba04fafaaa7ea8eb.poster.avif?t=1771250516\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327640/extras/3ac3eb9db6f903c2ba04fafaaa7ea8eb.webm?t=1771250516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327640/extras/3ac3eb9db6f903c2ba04fafaaa7ea8eb.mp4?t=1771250516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >发展你的基地</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁新的物品、角色和派系，与之互动——从冷酷无情的骑士团到无所不知的 PFS。实验与制造协同效应带来的可能性是无限的：两次远征绝不会给你相同的感觉。</p>",
